page.title: 11RAY FARM HIGH WYCOMBE
page.content: The farmer was born at Winchbotton Farm in a wattle and daub house with a slate roof.The{landscape}around is mainly grass.He went to the Church of England School in High Wycombe.His{ {attitude}to life is that it has changed for the better. His{home life}was hard.He would collect bottles and take them to a pub to sell.Then he would spend 3d and have 3d on the cinema.Then he would give the rest of the money to his mother for some food. The farmer was born on the land which belonged to the Marquis of Lincoln.
